Removed api.html as it is no longer needed.

Made the code run in python3

Replaced all instances of #!/usr/bin/python with #!/usr/bin/env python3
This prevents people from mistakenly running the code as python2

defined source code encoding to UTF-8

The character '–' was causing the app to crash due to it being non-ASCII.
Encoding the source code as UTF-8 fixes this.
